data.description: 3-bedroom 2 bath home situated on 1.17 acres with horse privileges offers 1,240 sq ft if living space and plenty of room to park the RV! Looking for a home with an assumable interest rate well below today's current rates? Come and check out this home and it's beautiful mountain views! Carpets have just been professionally cleaned and it's ready for the new owners!  Other important features and upgrades include: *Covered carport parking *Open floor plan *Ceiling fans *Casual dining *Breakfast bar *Indoor laundry *Master bedroom with single vanity and walk-in shower *Two guest bedrooms with full guest bath *Storage shed *Covered back patio with fenced back yard! Just minutes from Kingman and about 25 minutes to Bullhead City, the Colorado River, Lake Mohave and the casinos of Laughlin NV! Seller has assumable VA loan at 3.875%!  Property is in short sale, buyer will be responsible to pay septic inspection fee.
